com.psddev.dari.util

Class PullThroughCache<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psddev.dari.util.PullThroughCache<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<K,V>

    public abstract class PullThroughCache<K,V>
extends Object
implements Map<K,V>
    Read-only map implementation that produces its values on demand.

    Sub-classes must implement:

    • produce(K)

    Optionally, they can further override:

    • isExpired(K, java.util.Date)
